title: Local Black Stars hero Joel Fameyeh thrilled with sparkling display in CHAN qualifier
text:
14:25 CET Local Black Stars hero Joel Fameyeh thrilled with sparkling display in CHAN qualifier - www.ghanasoccernet.com 
Local Black Stars hero Joel Fameyeh is delighted with his headline-grabbing display in Sunday's 2016 CHAN qualifier against Ivory Coast in Kumasi. 
The player from the Division One League scored a brace as Ghana rallied to gain a slim first leg advantage in a 2-1 victory at Baba Yara Stadium. 
For more Ghana football news visit www.ghanasoccernet.com
